                                    <h3 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">#2 치료 및 원인 별 관리법</button></h3>
